title: Student Spotlight: Gisela Alonso | University of Science and Arts of Oklahoma

organizations.name: USAO
quotes: Recognized on the USAO honor roll for two semesters, Alonso is determined to continue her academic achievements and remain on that list throughout the remainder of her time at the university.
USAO has many clubs and job opportunities that can give you experience for the future,” she said. “They really help students beef up their resumes and skills for the real world.”
